```bash
find . -name "LoopVectorize.cpp"
```
The file is at `./llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/LoopVectorize.cpp`. I will now construct the `sed` command to insert the check.

```bash
sed -i '/Value \*EPResumeVal = SCEV2Value.lookup(EPResumeSCEV);/a \
  if (!EPResumeVal) {\
    Plan.clear();\
    return;\
  }' llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/LoopVectorize.cpp
